Insider Activity


Individual




L. Melvin Cooper



Mr. L. M. Cooper, CPA, is Independent Director at Par Pacific Holdings, Inc., Independent Director at Flotek Industries, Inc., Chief Financial Officer, Secretary & Senior VP at Forbes Energy Services LLC, and Chief Financial Officer, Senior VP & Secretary at Forbes Energy Services Ltd. He is on the Board of Directors at Par Pacific Holdings, Inc., Flotek Industries, Inc., and NACD Texas Tricities Chapter.
Mr. Cooper was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by Cude Oilfield Contractors, Inc., President by SpectraSource Corp., President & Chief Executive Officer by Cerqa, Inc., and Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by Nationwide Argosy Solutions LLC.
He received his undergraduate degree from Texas A&M University-Kingsville.



